title: Angels slowed with 8-7 loss to Athletics
text: Angels slowed with 8-7 loss to Athletics Thursday, 1 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) One day after the Angels completed a two-month chase by passing Houston for the second AL wild-card spot, Los Angeles committed four errors and gave up seven unearned runs in an 8-7 loss to the Oakland Athletics on Wednesday night that further complicated the AL playoff race.
